# Per-context AWS LoadBalancer security groups for istio-ingressgateway (see istio-setup/004).
# SG IDs are VPC-scoped — use a different list per kube/oc context when clusters sit in different VPCs.
#
# Format (one row per context):  context|replace-SGs|extra-SGs
#   - Fields are pipe-separated (|).
#   - replace-SGs → annotation aws-load-balancer-security-groups (replaces default LB SGs).
#   - extra-SGs   → annotation aws-load-balancer-extra-security-groups (additive).
#   - Leave a field empty to fall through to per-context env vars or global AWS_LOAD_BALANCER_* in versions.env.
#   - Use "-" in a field to force omitting that annotation for this context (overrides globals).
#
# rosa-001|sg-aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa,sg-bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb|
# rosa-002||sg-ccccccccccccccccc
# rosa-003|-|sg-ddddddddddddddddd
